name: RUMINATE VOL. 1
description: My second self-published zine! Made after Nude & Crude Vol. 1! In the making since 2011, here's a collection of my favorite drawings I've ever doodled. Some didn't make the cut, but that's for Vol. 2. Take a look at what my mind looks like visually and delve into a dreamy sub-conscious of my art.

name: Nude & Crude Vol. 1
description:
My first self-published zine I made over this summer! This is for the 18+ crowd, NSFW, and XXX. A short but thought-provoking intro detailing my inspiration for creating this zine, and 36 pages (front to back) doodles of very provocative poses of nude women! Front and Back cover printed on card stock, and printed on New Leaf paper.

Limited quantities!
